@Reasoning:
A list emits '[a, b, c]' or '[h | tail]' when a cons tail is present.
@End Reasoning
Process called "generate_list" takes context as Integer, node as Integer returns Integer:
    proc out_char with context, 91
    Let elements be proc get_dict_hir_value with node, "elements"
    proc generate_expr_list with context, elements
    Let tail be proc get_dict_hir_value with node, "tail"
    If tail is not equal to 0:
        proc out_str with context, " | "
